## Conclusion
The project already has Vercel Web Analytics properly installed and configured according to the latest official documentation. The implementation:
- Uses the correct package (`@vercel/analytics@2.0.1`)
- Imports from the correct module (`@vercel/analytics/next`)
- Places the component in the correct location (root layout)
- Follows Next.js App Router best practices

**No code changes were necessary.** The analytics will be active once the application is deployed to Vercel with analytics enabled in the dashboard.

## Next Steps for Deployment
To enable analytics tracking in production:
1. Deploy the application to Vercel
2. Navigate to Analytics in the Vercel dashboard
3. Click "Enable" to activate Web Analytics
4. Verify tracking by checking the Network tab for requests to `/_vercel/insights/*`
